    <briefdescription>
<para>Controlling Pebble&apos;s backlight </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The Light API provides you with functions to turn on Pebble’s backlight or put it back into automatic control. You can trigger the backlight and schedule a timer to automatically disable the backlight after a short delay, which is the preferred method of interacting with the backlight. </para>
